    "ML technologies have significantly advanced these fields; however, unique challenges persist.",
    "For example, the imbalance in natural datasets is problematic in many cases, possibly causing misevaluation or misinterpretation.",
    "Effective approaches to address this problem include data augmentation, simultaneous use of domain knowledge, and transfer learning.",
